{
  "id": "adv_main_01_08_09",
  "title": "星見編2章14話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "今日会った人の話っていうのがね\n――私を、ミュージカルにスカウトしたいそうなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ about the person I met today‚\n――apparently‚ she wants to recruit me for a musical.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.133333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 8.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……そう、遙子さんと会っていた女性は）\n（ ミュージカル劇団の座長だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That’s right. The woman who met with Haruko-san）\n（was the head of a musical troupe.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.033333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんの歌唱力とダンスをミュージカルで）\n（ 生かしてみないか……という勧誘だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She made an offer to use Haruko-san's）\n（singing and dancing skills in a musical.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ミュージカル、すごいなぁ。一度も観たことないから\n……聞いてるだけでドキドキしちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A musical‚ wow! I’ve never been to one before.\nIt makes me excited just to think about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.500000000000007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ミュージカルは演技だけじゃなく、歌えて踊れないと\nいけないから、声がかかるのは納得出来るけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Musicals aren’t just about acting. You have to be able\nto sing and dance‚ so it makes sense they’d approach you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.493265247344972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "座長さんもそう言ってた\n実際、アイドルから転向してくる人も多いみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what she said as well.\nApparently‚ there are a lot of idols who've switched over to musicals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7531971613566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "演技には……まだ、自信はないけど\nこれまでダンスと歌で表現力は磨いてきたつもりだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m still not that confident about my acting‚\nbut I’ve trained hard to express myself through dancing and singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.28653049468992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "挑戦してみるのも悪くはないかな、って\nちょっとだけ思ったの……ちょっとだけね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I did briefly consider that it might be worth\ngiving it a shot……just briefly though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.55319716135659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（これまで遙子さんは、ひたすら努力を続けてきた）\n（ 鳴かず飛ばずな日々が続いても、腐ることなく）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Up until now‚ Haruko-san has continued to work hard‚）\n（never slacking off‚ despite not gaining much popularity.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.683141136169425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（決して諦めずに頑張ってきた）\n（ それは、いつか大舞台に立つチャンスを得るためだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She never gave up and kept pushing forward as it was ）\n（all in the hope of one day getting a chance on the big stage.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8831411361694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、嬉しかったの\n私のこと……見てくれてる人がいたんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ it made me happy to know\nthere was someone out there watching my performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5831411361694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ遙子さん……\n辞めちゃうの？ サニピ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ Haruko-san‚\nare you going to quit Sunny Peace?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.58314113616942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "……正直、悩んでるの\nまだ答えは出ていないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I’m still not sure.\nI don’t have an answer yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.91647446950275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "だからミュージカルの話は、一旦持ち帰ってきたの\nしっかり考えようかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I didn’t say yes on the spot.\nI wanted some time to think about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.84980780283607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……前に、親戚に言われてたことが\n結構引っかかっちゃってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing is… I keep remembering something\nmy relatives once told me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.51647446950275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "言われたこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did they tell you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.58314113616942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 102.11642913818358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは……\n若いうちしか出来ないでしょ……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being an idol…\n…is something you can only do while you’re young.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.24976247151692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないって思うし、否定もしたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think that’s true‚ and I disagreed at the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.78309580485023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "でも……今回のNEXT VENUSグランプリの\n応募総数、すごく多いでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… there are a ton of entries for this year’s\nNEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.20520458221436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "私より若い子もたくさんいる中で、年上の私がサニピに\nいたら、埋もれちゃうんじゃないかな……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With plenty of the girls being younger than me‚\nI’m worried I won’t stand out at my age here in Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0052045822144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "そう考えると、いいキッカケかなって思いつつ\nでも踏ん切りもつかなくって、どうしよっかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I think of it that way‚ this does seem like a good opportunity‚\nbut I still haven’t been able to make up my mind yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5385379155479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなに悩んでいたのか……いや）\n（ 俺達が気付かなかっただけで、一人ずっと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’d no idea she’s been worrying so much over this.）\n（She must’ve felt this way for a while‚ we just didn’t realize it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8052045822145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私……いやです\n遙子ちゃんに、アイドル辞めてほしくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m….against it.\nI don’t want you to quit being an idol‚ Haruko-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3718712488811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるけど\nそれは遙子さん自身が決めることで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get how you feel‚\nbut it’s Haruko-san’s decision to make.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4052045822143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "分かってる……でもせっかくこうして\n仲間になれたのに……始まったばかりなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know… but we’ve finally become a team‚\nand we’re just getting started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.63853791554763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan… thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6052045822143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん私も\n簡単に決めていいことじゃないって、分かってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I understand\nit’s not a decision to be made lightly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.00520458221416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "だからもう少しだけ……考えさせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please… give me a little more time to think about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.17187124888085,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.666666666737,
          "startTime": 178.93853791554758
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_09-skr005.m4a",
